        {
            "title": "美駐日大使稱美國會在任何中日爭端中力挺日本",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"美駐日大使稱美國會在任何中日爭端中力挺日本\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/BBEi8wMQnHe2.kI60GT.aA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-11/70a564c0-c60c-11f0-b6eb-ec5b2986c913\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">美駐日大使稱美國會在任何中日爭端中力挺日本</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E9%A7%90%E6%97%A5%E5%A4%A7%E4%BD%BF%E7%A8%B1%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E6%9C%83%E5%9C%A8%E4%BB%BB%E4%BD%95%E4%B8%AD%E6%97%A5%E7%88%AD%E7%AB%AF%E4%B8%AD%E5%8A%9B%E6%8C%BA%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC-085411606.html",
